{"timestamp":"00:00:13.543","source":"Server","level":"LOG","message":"Full Signal Data: \"{\\n  \\\"title\\\": \\\"AI Startups Raised $550M Last Week - MLQ.ai\\\",\\n  \\\"description\\\": \\\"AI Startups Raised $550M Last Week\\\\n\\\\n# AI Startups Raised $550M Last Week\\\\n\\\\nPeter Foy\\\\nAI Startups Raised $550M Last Week\\\\n\\\\nWelcome to our roundup of the top stories & startups to watch in AI, this week we have stories on:\\\\n\\\\n## This Week in AI 🗞️\\\\n\\\\nThis week in AI, publicly-traded AI companies lost market share after earnings reports and investors seem to be prioritizing performance over AI potential.\\\\n\\\\nAI companies lost $190B last week 📉\\\\n\\\\n'Magnificent Seven' market grip slips 7️⃣\\\\n\\\\n## AI Startups Raised $550M 🚀\\\\n\\\\nAI startups raised a total of $550M+ in venture funding this past week, here are a few of our favourite to watch.\\\\n\\\\nCodeium\\\\n\\\\nKore.ai\\\\n\\\\nDataSnipper\\\\n\\\\nAlign AI [...] Codeium\\\\n\\\\nKore.ai\\\\n\\\\nDataSnipper\\\\n\\\\nAlign AI\\\\n\\\\nThat's it for this edition of This Week in AI, if you were forwarded this newsletter and would like to receive it you can sign up below.\\\\n\\\\n## Sign up for MLQ.ai\\\\n\\\\nWe’re a group of machine learning engineers & quantitative analysts. We apply AI & LLMs to financial markets and track every VC deal each week. Sign up below to get started.\\\\n\\\\nNo spam. Unsubscribe anytime.\\\\n\\\\n## Spread the word\\\\n\\\\n## Google Launches Gemini Advanced\\\\n\\\\n## 20+ Midjourney Web Design Prompts\\\\n\\\\n## Keep reading\\\\n\\\\n### Google Releases Gemini 2.5 - This Week in AI\\\\n\\\\n### AI Startups Raised $15B+ Last Week\\\\n\\\\n### AI Startups Raised $1.4B Last Week\\\\n\\\\n### Subscribe to our newsletter\\\\n\\\\nStay updated with MLQ.ai by signing up for our newsletter.\\\",\\n  \\\"url\\\": \\\"https://blog.mlq.ai/ai-startups-raised-550m-last-week/\\\",\\n  \\\"trigger_type\\\": \\\"funding\\\",\\n  \\\"confidence_score\\\": 34,\\n  \\\"score_reasoning\\\": \\\"Notable signal based on and industry source coverage, funding, raised, cautionary signals\\\",\\n  \\\"published_date\\\": null,\\n  \\\"source\\\": \\\"blog.mlq.ai\\\",\\n  \\\"status\\\": \\\"new\\\",\\n  \\\"category\\\": \\\"Funding\\\",\\n  \\\"created_at\\\": \\\"2026-04-26T11:26:39.303Z\\\"\\n}\""}
