{"timestamp":"00:00:13.777","source":"Server","level":"LOG","message":"Full Signal Data: \"{\\n  \\\"title\\\": \\\"The Agentic AI Infrastructure Landscape in 2025 — 2026 - Medium\\\",\\n  \\\"description\\\": \\\"LangSmith leads with multi-turn evaluation capabilities, an Insights Agent that automatically categorizes failure modes across millions of traces, and framework-agnostic tracing. Braintrust, used by companies like Notion, Stripe, and Zapier, is the most CI/CD-native platform, offering a dedicated GitHub Action that turns every evaluation run into a full experiment with pull request commenting. Arize AI, which raised a $70M Series C in early 2025, provides enterprise-grade observability through its open-source Phoenix tool, built on OpenTelemetry and OpenInference standards — which have become the de facto standard for agent tracing. Langfuse’s acquisition by ClickHouse in early 2026 validated the thesis that AI observability is becoming core database infrastructure. [...] Mem0, which raised a $24M Series A in October 2025 and was chosen as AWS’s exclusive memory provider, takes a hybrid datastore approach that combines vector, key-value, and graph stores. It has demonstrated notably higher accuracy and dramatically lower latency on established memory benchmarks compared to alternatives. Zep, through its Graphiti system, builds on temporal knowledge graphs with a bi-temporal model that tracks both when events occurred and when they were ingested, enabling sophisticated temporal reasoning. [...] Meta takes a distinct approach, powering the ecosystem through open-weights models rather than owning the runtime layer.\\\",\\n  \\\"url\\\": \\\"https://medium.com/@vinniesmandava/the-agentic-ai-infrastructure-landscape-in-2025-2026-a-strategic-analysis-for-tool-builders-b0da8368aee2\\\",\\n  \\\"trigger_type\\\": \\\"tech_pivot\\\",\\n  \\\"confidence_score\\\": 36,\\n  \\\"score_reasoning\\\": \\\"Notable signal based on and industry source coverage, raised, acquisition, Series A Series C involving Series A Series C\\\",\\n  \\\"published_date\\\": null,\\n  \\\"source\\\": \\\"medium.com\\\",\\n  \\\"status\\\": \\\"new\\\",\\n  \\\"category\\\": \\\"TechPivot\\\",\\n  \\\"created_at\\\": \\\"2026-04-26T11:26:39.537Z\\\"\\n}\""}
