{"timestamp":"00:00:13.824","source":"Server","level":"LOG","message":"Full Signal Data: \"{\\n  \\\"title\\\": \\\"TOP 10 Agentic AI Development Companies In The US [2026]\\\",\\n  \\\"description\\\": \\\"### 10. IBM\\\\n\\\\nIBM is one of the world’s largest and most established technology companies, headquartered in Armonk, New York. With decades of experience in AI, it has evolved into a leading enterprise-level agentic AI provider. Beyond its engineering services, much of IBM’s agentic AI work runs on the watsonx platform, which includes pre-built components, orchestration tools, and governance frameworks built for large and complex enterprise environments. [...] Based in Florida with delivery teams in Ukraine, DevCom is an optimal choice for SMBs that want to work with leading companies in agentic AI development while still keeping the engagement flexible and efficient for their size. [...] Unique value proposition: IBM specializes in large-scale, compliant agentic AI deployments for Fortune 500 companies, government agencies, and highly regulated industries. With strong governance, pre-built agent accelerators, and industry-specific frameworks, it’s ideal for organizations that require strict security and multi-department automation.\\\",\\n  \\\"url\\\": \\\"https://devcom.com/tech-blog/top-agentic-ai-development-companies-in-the-usa/\\\",\\n  \\\"trigger_type\\\": \\\"tech_pivot\\\",\\n  \\\"confidence_score\\\": 31,\\n  \\\"score_reasoning\\\": \\\"Notable signal based on and industry source coverage, cautionary signals, new york tech hub in new york\\\",\\n  \\\"published_date\\\": null,\\n  \\\"source\\\": \\\"devcom.com\\\",\\n  \\\"status\\\": \\\"new\\\",\\n  \\\"category\\\": \\\"TechPivot\\\",\\n  \\\"created_at\\\": \\\"2026-04-26T11:26:39.584Z\\\"\\n}\""}
