{"timestamp":"00:00:14.103","source":"Server","level":"LOG","message":"Full Signal Data: \"{\\n  \\\"title\\\": \\\"10 Best Agentic AI Companies to Watch in 2026 - Straive\\\",\\n  \\\"description\\\": \\\"### USERReady\\\\n\\\\nUSERReady applies Agentic AI to accelerate analytics and reporting workflows. Its agents interact directly with enterprise data systems to streamline insight generation. Rapid, repeatable deployments highlight its operational maturity.\\\\n\\\\n## Why Do These Companies Lead the Agentic AI Landscape?\\\\n\\\\nThe companies shaping the Agentic AI landscape deliver more than automation. They build intelligent systems that understand goals, coordinate multiple agents, and respond to real business conditions. This enables organizations to operate more efficiently and with greater consistency. [...] ## FAQ’s\\\\n\\\\nAgentic AI refers to autonomous systems that can make decisions, take actions, and complete tasks without constant human input. Unlike traditional tools that wait for instructions, these systems understand business goals, sense real-time events, and execute tasks within enterprise workflow\\\\n\\\\nWhile Generative AI models focus on creating content and insights, they typically stop at providing recommendations. Agentic AI bridges the gap between intelligence and execution by running processes end-to-end, reacting to new data instantly, and managing outcomes with minimal oversight. [...] Straive\\\\n\\\\n### Powered By Agentic AI\\\\n\\\\n# 10 Best Agentic AI Companies to Watch in 2026\\\\n\\\\nPosted on: Decmeber 1st 2025\\\\n\\\\n2025 became the year enterprises stopped experimenting and began treating autonomy as a strategic priority. As adoption accelerated, the market made one thing clear: agentic AI companies are no longer operating on the fringe; they’re shaping how modern enterprises run.\\\\n\\\\nLeaders moved beyond pilot projects and began embedding intelligent systems into real workflows, seeking solutions that could act, make decisions, and deliver outcomes with minimal intervention. According to McKinsey’s State of AI: Global Survey 2025, 23% of organizations are already scaling agentic AI systems, reinforcing the shift toward autonomy and the growing confidence in AI-driven execution.\\\",\\n  \\\"url\\\": \\\"https://www.straive.com/blogs/top-agentic-ai-companies-2026/\\\",\\n  \\\"trigger_type\\\": \\\"tech_pivot\\\",\\n  \\\"confidence_score\\\": 28,\\n  \\\"score_reasoning\\\": \\\"Notable signal based on and industry source coverage, cautionary signals, comprehensive analysis\\\",\\n  \\\"published_date\\\": null,\\n  \\\"source\\\": \\\"straive.com\\\",\\n  \\\"status\\\": \\\"new\\\",\\n  \\\"category\\\": \\\"TechPivot\\\",\\n  \\\"created_at\\\": \\\"2026-04-26T11:26:39.862Z\\\"\\n}\""}
