{"timestamp":"00:00:14.238","source":"Server","level":"LOG","message":"Full Signal Data: \"{\\n  \\\"title\\\": \\\"These Tech Companies Announced New Boston Headquarters in 2023 | Built In Boston\\\",\\n  \\\"description\\\": \\\"### Zoovu\\\\n\\\\nView Profile\\\\n\\\\nFounded in Austria, Zoovu helps consumers find companies’ products more easily through its natural language processing software. Its product discovery solution uses data to deduce what a customer might be looking for. The artificial intelligence company announced its new global headquarters in Boston in March. This news follows an investment from FTV Capital and the appointment of a new CEO James Novak last year.\\\\n\\\\n\\\\n\\\\n### Sasaki\\\\n\\\\nView Profile [...] Built In Logo Built In Logo\\\\n\\\\nGlobal Tech Hub\\\\n\\\\nBuiltIn.com is the global destination for tech professionals.\\\\n\\\\nbuiltin.com\\\\n\\\\nPopular Tech Hubs\\\\n\\\\nUnited StatesAustinBostonChicagoColoradoLos AngelesNew York CitySeattleSan Francisco\\\\n\\\\nAustraliaSydneyMelbourne\\\\n\\\\nCanadaCalgaryMontrealOttawaQuebecTorontoVancouver\\\\n\\\\nIndiaBengaluruChennaiDelhiHyderabadKolkataMumbaiPune\\\\n\\\\nIrelandDublin\\\\n\\\\nSingaporeSingapore\\\\n\\\\nUnited KingdomLondonCambridgeManchesterBirminghamBristol\\\\n\\\\nCompany Photo Can't find your company?\\\\n\\\\nCreate a company profile.\\\\n\\\\nView All Jobs\\\\n\\\\n Hire on Built In\\\\n Post a Job\\\\n\\\\nJoin\\\\n\\\\nLog In\\\\n\\\\n# These Tech Companies Announced New Boston Headquarters in 2023\\\\n\\\\nFind out which tech companies plan to relocate to the East Coast this year.\\\\n\\\\nWritten by Ashley Bowden\\\\n\\\\nPublished on Apr. 17, 2023 [...] ### Product Insight\\\\n\\\\nView Profile\\\\n\\\\nSpecializing in designing and engineering products for sectors like biotech, Product Insight is relocating its firm’s headquarters from Acton, Georgia to Boxborough, according to an April announcement. The move to the Tech Central building at 80 Central St. aims to better suit Product Insight’s facility requirements. The building spans 149,000 square feet in size, and Product Insight will lease 21,000 square feet.\\\\n\\\\n\\\\n\\\\n### Zoovu\\\\n\\\\nView Profile\\\",\\n  \\\"url\\\": \\\"https://www.builtinboston.com/articles/boston-headquarters-openings-2023\\\",\\n  \\\"trigger_type\\\": \\\"expansion\\\",\\n  \\\"confidence_score\\\": 34,\\n  \\\"score_reasoning\\\": \\\"Notable signal based on and industry source coverage, investment, cautionary signals in boston\\\",\\n  \\\"published_date\\\": null,\\n  \\\"source\\\": \\\"builtinboston.com\\\",\\n  \\\"status\\\": \\\"new\\\",\\n  \\\"category\\\": \\\"Expansion\\\",\\n  \\\"created_at\\\": \\\"2026-04-26T11:26:39.998Z\\\"\\n}\""}
