{"timestamp":"00:00:14.339","source":"Server","level":"LOG","message":"Full Signal Data: \"{\\n  \\\"title\\\": \\\"ASM Technologies Expands Global Footprint with Launch of New Atlanta Office - ASM Technologies\\\",\\n  \\\"description\\\": \\\"ASM Technologies today announced the official opening of its brand-new, state-of-the-art office in Munich, marking a significant milestone in the company’s European growth journey.\\\\n\\\\nThis expansion reflects ASM’s long-term commitment to:\\\\n\\\\n Delivering innovative hardware and software solutions tailored to client needs.\\\\n Helping organisations streamline procurement and manage tail spend more effectively.\\\\n Building lasting in-channel partnerships with vendors and clients in territory.\\\\n\\\\nThe new Munich office will serve as a central hub for collaboration, enabling ASM to coordinate more closely with regional teams, share expertise more effectively, and deliver faster, more integrated support for clients across Germany and continental Europe. [...] Iain Tomkinson, Chief Revenue Officer at ASM Technologies, commented:\\\\n\\\\n> Opening our Munich office represents an exciting step forward in ASM’s growth journey. Germany is a key market for us, and this investment reflects our commitment to supporting our clients and partners with local expertise, while driving innovation and efficiency across the channel. Our Munich team will be instrumental in shaping the next chapter of our European expansion.\\\\n\\\\nASM’s Munich office launch underscores the company’s continued momentum in expanding its international presence, ensuring proximity to key markets, and providing a platform for further innovation and collaboration.\\\\n\\\\nRead article\\\\n\\\\n##### ASM Celebrates Record Sales, Exceeding £100m For The First Time In Our History [...] What We Do\\\\n  + Tail Spend\\\\n Our Customers\\\\n Our Vendors\\\\n Who We Are\\\\n  + Our Story\\\\n  + Our Mission & Values\\\\n  + Our People\\\\n  + Our Locations\\\\n  + Quality & Accreditations\\\\n  + Environment & CSR\\\\n Whats New?\\\\n  + News & Events\\\\n Careers\\\\n\\\\n##### News & Events\\\\n\\\\n# ASM Technologies Expands Global Footprint with Launch of New Atlanta Office\\\\n\\\\nASM Technologies is proud to announce the opening of its new North American office in Atlanta, Georgia, a key milestone in the company’s continued global expansion. The new location places ASM at the center of one of the U.S.’s most dynamic technology hubs, reinforcing its commitment to delivering exceptional service and support to clients across the region.\\\",\\n  \\\"url\\\": \\\"https://asmtech.com/uk/asm-technologies-expands-global-footprint-with-launch-of-new-atlanta-office/\\\",\\n  \\\"trigger_type\\\": \\\"expansion\\\",\\n  \\\"confidence_score\\\": 44,\\n  \\\"score_reasoning\\\": \\\"Notable signal based on and industry source coverage, expansion, investment, positive momentum\\\",\\n  \\\"published_date\\\": null,\\n  \\\"source\\\": \\\"asmtech.com\\\",\\n  \\\"status\\\": \\\"new\\\",\\n  \\\"category\\\": \\\"Expansion\\\",\\n  \\\"created_at\\\": \\\"2026-04-26T11:26:40.103Z\\\"\\n}\""}
